title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

AFFORDABLE QUALITY AUTO REPAIR [From a sign in Kailua, Hawaii. Submitted by Mary M. Tius.]

“Downtown Minneapolis is going to be like the State Fair, only no admission to get in.” [From the Minneapolis Star Tribune, March 27, 2001, page C6. Submitted by Robert Farlee.]
